OL,3,CWhy didn't Lindsay Hoyle chair the
OL,4,CBudget and who is the Deputy Speaker?
OL,6,FGhani is the senior Deputy Speaker,
OL,7,Fand is the first ethnic minority MP to
OL,8,Fbe elected to the position.
OL,10,FShe is one of three Deputy Speakers -
OL,11,FJudith Cummins and Caroline Nokes were
OL,12,Falso elected in July.
OL,14,FHowever, they each have different
OL,15,Froles, and Cummins and Nokes were
OL,16,Felected to First Deputy and Second
OL,17,FDeputy Chairman of Ways and Means,
OL,18,Frespectively.
