OL,3,CWhy didn't Lindsay Hoyle chair the
OL,4,CBudget and who is the Deputy Speaker?
OL,6,FThis is the first time ever there is
OL,7,Fan all-female line-up of Deputy
OL,8,FSpeakers.
OL,10,FWhat does the Deputy Speaker do?
OL,12,FAll three of the Deputies assist the
OL,13,FSpeaker in his duties.
OL,15,FThe senior Deputy Speaker, who is the
OL,16,FChairman of the Ways and Means, is
OL,17,Felected from the opposite side of the
OL,18,FHouse to the Speaker.
