OL,3,CWhy didn't Lindsay Hoyle chair the
OL,4,CBudget and who is the Deputy Speaker?
OL,6,FThey are responsible for chairing the
OL,7,Fbudget, the selection of amendments
OL,8,Fduring Committee of the whole House
OL,9,Fand supervising business in
OL,10,FWestminster Hall, the House of
OL,11,FCommons' parallel chamber, according
OL,12,Fto the UK Parliament website.
OL,14,FWhy does the Deputy Speaker chair the
OL,15,FBudget statement?
OL,17,FUp until the 18th century the position
OL,18,Fof Speaker was one that came with
OL,19,Fsignificant danger and at times was
OL,20,Funtenable.
