OL,3,CWhy didn't Lindsay Hoyle chair the
OL,4,CBudget and who is the Deputy Speaker?
OL,6,FWho is Deputy Speaker Nusrat Ghani?
OL,8,FNusrat Ghani is the Conservative MP
OL,9,Ffor Sussex Weald.
OL,11,FShe was elected in 2015, and has
OL,12,Fpreviously held Ministerial positions
OL,13,Fin the Foreign, Commonwealth and
OL,14,FDevelopment Office and Department for
OL,15,FBusiness and Trade.
OL,17,FGhani made history after she was
OL,18,Fbecame the first ethnic minority MP to
OL,19,Fbe elected to the role of Deputy
OL,20,FSpeaker.
